00:04:45.502 --> 00:04:48.380
That's why Jews can't stand us Christians,

00:04:48.588 --> 00:04:50.966
that's why they killed Christ.

00:04:51.049 --> 00:04:52.550
And that's why I can't stand them.

00:04:52.634 --> 00:04:54.719
Do you know what I do with pork-haters?

00:04:54.802 --> 00:04:55.470
We don't.

00:04:55.553 --> 00:04:58.556
