00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:01.393
Better a Jew without a beard than a beard without a Jew!

00:05:01.476 --> 00:05:03.228
Do you know what they do in Moldova?

00:05:03.311 --> 00:05:04.980
I don't know...

00:05:05.063 --> 00:05:10.318
Jews walk around in their carriages.

00:05:10.402 --> 00:05:12.404
