00:05:15.949 --> 00:05:18.911
I don't believe it, father.That's what the Russians did to us.

00:05:18.952 --> 00:05:20.578
In the war of 1828,

00:05:20.662 --> 00:05:23.081
General Zaltukhin harnessed our peasants...

00:05:23.165 --> 00:05:26.001
The Christians in my cousin's village

00:05:26.126 --> 00:05:28.670
